description:
To test following functionality in customer center role.
    1. To verify filter search functionality.
    2. To select number of layer with dynamic changes rows.
    3. To verify language selection and according change language to all pages.
    4. To verify company name and display record as per comapny selection.
    5. TO verify label and insert new template with existing and multiple template record in a database.
    6. To verify list of template and search functionality in all columns.
    7. Select no of layer and dynamic add enter no added row or not.
    8. Create new joint request and displayed in joints list and also search functionality check.
    9. To verify search customer record.
    10. Sent to application team request.
    11. To verify logout functionality.
